Gilbert Belnap - A black and white photo of a man with a beard

Photo of Gilbert Belnap, a Mormon pioneer, LDS Church leader, and an early colonizer of Ogden, Utah, Fort Lemhi, Idaho and Hooper, Utah.

William R. Smith (Mormon)

Photo of William R. Smith a Utah territorial politician and a leader of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints (LDS Church) in Utah Territory.

Zina Young Card Brown - A black and white photo of a woman with glasse...

Photograph of Zina Young Card Brown, wife of Hugh B. Brown. Hugh B. Brown a member of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles and the First Presidency of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints (LDS Church).

Robert T. Burton - A black and white photo of a man with a long beard

Photo of Robert T. Burton, a member of the presiding bishopric of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints (LDS Church) from 1874 until his death. He was also one of the principal officers in the Nauvoo ... More
